snippet.title: Sticky Business - Official Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
Get another look at Sticky Business, an upcoming small business simulation game all about making stickers and creating memorable customer experiences. In Sticky Business, create stickers with thousands of customization options, pack orders, develop your online store, and build customer relationships. Sticky Business is coming to PC via Steam in Summer 2023.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
